<h2 id="2-二重积分"><a href="#2-二重积分" class="headerlink" title="2. 二重积分"></a>2. 二重积分</h2><h3 id="2-1-直角坐标"><a href="#2-1-直角坐标" class="headerlink" title="2.1 直角坐标"></a>2.1 直角坐标</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\iint_Sf(x,y)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y=\int_{x_1}^{x_2}\mathrm{d}x\int_{y_1(x)}^{y_2(x)}f(x,y)\mathrm{d}y
$$
</div>

<h3 id="2-2-极坐标"><a href="#2-2-极坐标" class="headerlink" title="2.2 极坐标"></a>2.2 极坐标</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\iint_Sf(x,y)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y=\iint_Ef(r\cos\theta,r\sin\theta)r\mathrm{d}r\mathrm{d}\theta
$$
</div>

<h3 id="2-3-变量替换"><a href="#2-3-变量替换" class="headerlink" title="2.3 变量替换"></a>2.3 变量替换</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\iint_Sf(x,y)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y=\iint_Ef(x(u,v),y(u,v))\cdot\left|\mathrm{det}\frac{\partial(x,y)}{\partial(u,v)}\right|\mathrm{d}u\mathrm{d}v
$$
</div>

<h2 id="3-三重积分"><a href="#3-三重积分" class="headerlink" title="3. 三重积分"></a>3. 三重积分</h2><h3 id="3-1-直角坐标"><a href="#3-1-直角坐标" class="headerlink" title="3.1 直角坐标"></a>3.1 直角坐标</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\iiint_\Omega f(x,y,z)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y\mathrm{d}z=\iint_{\Omega_{xy}}\left[\int_{z_1(x,y)}^{z_2(x,y)}f(x,y,z)\mathrm{d}z\right]\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y=\int_{z_1}^{z_2}\mathrm{d}z\iint_{\Omega_{xy}}f(x,y,z)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y
$$
</div>

<h3 id="3-2-柱坐标"><a href="#3-2-柱坐标" class="headerlink" title="3.2 柱坐标"></a>3.2 柱坐标</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\begin{cases}
x=r\cos\theta\\
y=r\sin\theta\\
z=z
\end{cases}
$$
</div>

<div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\iiint_\Omega f(x,y,z)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y\mathrm{d}z=\iiint_{\Omega^*}f(r\cos\theta,r\sin\theta,z)r\mathrm{d}r\mathrm{d}\theta\mathrm{d}z
$$
</div>

<h3 id="3-3-球坐标"><a href="#3-3-球坐标" class="headerlink" title="3.3 球坐标"></a>3.3 球坐标</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\begin{cases}
x=\rho\sin\varphi\cos\theta\\
y=\rho\sin\varphi\sin\theta\\
z=\rho\cos\varphi
\end{cases},\varphi\in[0,\pi],\theta\in[0,2\pi]
$$
</div>
<div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\iiint_\Omega f(x,y,z)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y\mathrm{d}z=\iiint_{\Omega^*}f(\rho\sin\varphi\cos\theta,\rho\sin\varphi\sin\theta,\rho\cos\varphi)\rho^2\sin\varphi\mathrm{d}\rho\mathrm{d}\varphi\mathrm{d}\theta
$$
</div>

<h3 id="3-4-变量替换"><a href="#3-4-变量替换" class="headerlink" title="3.4 变量替换"></a>3.4 变量替换</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\iiint_\Omega f(x,y,z)=\iiint_{\Omega^*}f(x(u,v,w),y(u,v,w),z(u,v,w))\cdot\left|\mathrm{det}\frac{\partial(x,y,z)}{\partial(u,v,w)}\right|\mathrm{d}u\mathrm{d}v\mathrm{d}w
$$
</div>

<h2 id="4-重积分的应用"><a href="#4-重积分的应用" class="headerlink" title="4. 重积分的应用"></a>4. 重积分的应用</h2><h3 id="4-1-曲面面积"><a href="#4-1-曲面面积" class="headerlink" title="4.1 曲面面积"></a>4.1 曲面面积</h3><div class="table-container">
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th style="text-align:center">曲面方程</th>
<th style="text-align:center">区域</th>
<th style="text-align:center">面积</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:center">$\boldsymbol{r}=\boldsymbol{r}(u,v)$</td>
<td style="text-align:center">$(u,v)\in D$</td>
<td style="text-align:center">$\iint_D\Vert\boldsymbol{r}’_u\times\boldsymbol{r}’_v\Vert\mathrm{d}u\mathrm{d}v$</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:center">$z=f(x,y)$</td>
<td style="text-align:center">$(x,y)\in D$</td>
<td style="text-align:center">$\iint_D\sqrt{1+{f’_x}^2+{f’_y}^2}\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y$</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 id="4-2-物体的质心"><a href="#4-2-物体的质心" class="headerlink" title="4.2 物体的质心"></a>4.2 物体的质心</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
M=\iiint_\Omega\rho(x,y,z)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y\mathrm{d}z
$$
</div>
<div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\boldsymbol{r}_c=\frac{\iiint_\Omega\boldsymbol{r}\cdot\rho(x,y,z)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y\mathrm{d}z}{\iiint_\Omega\rho(x,y,z)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y\mathrm{d}z}
$$
</div>


<h3 id="4-3-转动惯量"><a href="#4-3-转动惯量" class="headerlink" title="4.3 转动惯量"></a>4.3 转动惯量</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
J_x=\iiint_\Omega(y^2+z^2)\rho(x,y,z)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y\mathrm{d}z\\
J_y=\iiint_\Omega(z^2+x^2)\rho(x,y,z)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y\mathrm{d}z\\
J_z=\iiint_\Omega(x^2+y^2)\rho(x,y,z)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y\mathrm{d}z
$$
</div>

<h3 id="4-4-万有引力"><a href="#4-4-万有引力" class="headerlink" title="4.4 万有引力"></a>4.4 万有引力</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
F_x=\iiint_\Omega\frac{Gm_0(x-x_0)\rho(x,y,z)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y\mathrm{d}z}{\sqrt{(x-x_0)^2+(y-y_0)^2+(z-z_0)^2}^3}\\
F_y=\iiint_\Omega\frac{Gm_0(y-y_0)\rho(x,y,z)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y\mathrm{d}z}{\sqrt{(x-x_0)^2+(y-y_0)^2+(z-z_0)^2}^3}\\
F_z=\iiint_\Omega\frac{Gm_0(z-z_0)\rho(x,y,z)\mathrm{d}x\mathrm{d}y\mathrm{d}z}{\sqrt{(x-x_0)^2+(y-y_0)^2+(z-z_0)^2}^3}
$$
</div>

<h2 id="5-曲线积分"><a href="#5-曲线积分" class="headerlink" title="5. 曲线积分"></a>5. 曲线积分</h2><h3 id="5-1-第一型曲线积分"><a href="#5-1-第一型曲线积分" class="headerlink" title="5.1 第一型曲线积分"></a>5.1 第一型曲线积分</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\int_Lf\mathrm{d}l=\int_\alpha^\beta f(x(t),y(t),z(t))\cdot\sqrt{x'(t)^2+y'(t)^2+z'(t)^2}\mathrm{d}t
$$
</div>

<h3 id="5-2-第二型曲线积分"><a href="#5-2-第二型曲线积分" class="headerlink" title="5.2 第二型曲线积分"></a>5.2 第二型曲线积分</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\boldsymbol{\tau}=\frac{(x'(t),y'(t),z'(t))}{\sqrt{x'(t)^2+y'(t)^2+z'(t)^2}}\\
\mathrm{d}l=\sqrt{x'(t)^2+y'(t)^2+z'(t)^2}\mathrm{d}t\\
\boldsymbol{v}=(P(x,y,z),Q(x,y,z),R(x,y,z))
$$
</div>
<div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\int_L\boldsymbol{v}\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{l}=\int_L\boldsymbol{v}\cdot\boldsymbol{\tau}\mathrm{d}l=\pm\int_\alpha^\beta\left[Px'(t)+Qy'(t)+Rz'(t)\right]\mathrm{d}t
$$
</div>

<h2 id="6-曲面积分"><a href="#6-曲面积分" class="headerlink" title="6. 曲面积分"></a>6. 曲面积分</h2><h3 id="6-1-第一型曲面积分"><a href="#6-1-第一型曲面积分" class="headerlink" title="6.1 第一型曲面积分"></a>6.1 第一型曲面积分</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\iint_Sf(x,y,z)\mathrm{d}S=\iint_Df(x(u,v),y(u,v),z(u,v))\Vert\boldsymbol{r}'_u\times\boldsymbol{r}'_v\Vert\mathrm{d}u\mathrm{d}v
$$
</div>

<ul>
<li>Poisson公式<div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
S=\{(x,y,z)\vert x^2+y^2+z^2=1\}
$$
</div>
<div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\iint_Sf(ax+by+cz)\mathrm{d}S=2\pi\int_{-1}^1f(\sqrt{a^2+b^2+c^2}t)\mathrm{d}t
$$
</div>

</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="6-2-第二型曲面积分"><a href="#6-2-第二型曲面积分" class="headerlink" title="6.2 第二型曲面积分"></a>6.2 第二型曲面积分</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\boldsymbol{r}=\boldsymbol{r}(u,v)\,,\,\,\boldsymbol{r}'_u\times\boldsymbol{r}'_v=(A,B,C)\\
\boldsymbol{v}=(P,Q,R)
$$
</div>
<div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\iint_S\boldsymbol{v}\mathrm{d}\boldsymbol{S}=\pm\iint_S\frac{PA+QB+RC}{\sqrt{A^2+B^2+C^2}}\mathrm{d}S=\pm\iint_D(PA+QB+RC)\mathrm{d}u\mathrm{d}v
$$
</div>

<h2 id="7-Green公式及其应用"><a href="#7-Green公式及其应用" class="headerlink" title="7. Green公式及其应用"></a>7. Green公式及其应用</h2><h3 id="7-1-Green公式"><a href="#7-1-Green公式" class="headerlink" title="7.1 Green公式"></a>7.1 Green公式</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\oint_{\partial D}P\mathrm dx+Q\mathrm dy=\iint_D\left(\frac{\partial Q}{\partial x}-\frac{\partial P}{\partial y}\right)\mathrm dx\mathrm dy
$$
</div>

<blockquote>
<p>$\partial D$是有向曲线，沿$\partial D$正方向前进时，区域$D$总在左侧</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li>闭合曲线围成封闭区域的面积</li>
</ul>
<div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\sigma(D)=\iint_D\mathrm dx\mathrm dy=\oint_{\partial D}x\mathrm dy=-\oint_{\partial D}y\mathrm dx=\frac{1}{2}\oint_{\partial D}x\mathrm dy-y\mathrm dx
$$
</div>

<ul>
<li>Green公式的变形</li>
</ul>
<div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\oint_{\partial D}\boldsymbol v\cdot\boldsymbol \tau\mathrm dl=\iint_D\nabla\times\boldsymbol v\mathrm dx\mathrm dy\\
\oint_{\partial D}\boldsymbol v\cdot\boldsymbol n\mathrm dl=\iint_D\nabla\cdot\boldsymbol v\mathrm dx\mathrm dy
$$
</div>

<blockquote>
<p>梯度算子$\nabla=\left(\frac{\partial}{\partial x},\frac{\partial}{\partial y}\right)$，旋度算子$\nabla\times$，散度算子$\nabla\cdot$</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="7-2-平面向量场"><a href="#7-2-平面向量场" class="headerlink" title="7.2 平面向量场"></a>7.2 平面向量场</h3><ul>
<li>保守场$\boldsymbol u$：$\int_L\boldsymbol u\mathrm d\boldsymbol l$与路径无关</li>
<li>有势场$\boldsymbol u$ ：$\exists f,\boldsymbol u=\nabla f$</li>
<li>无源场$\boldsymbol u$：$\nabla\cdot \boldsymbol u=0$</li>
<li>无旋场$\boldsymbol u$：$\nabla\times\boldsymbol u=0$</li>
</ul>
<ol>
<li>连续的保守场等价于有势场</li>
<li>连续可微的保守场一定是无旋场</li>
<li>单连通区域上的连续可微保守场等价于无旋场</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="7-3-恰当方程"><a href="#7-3-恰当方程" class="headerlink" title="7.3 恰当方程"></a>7.3 恰当方程</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
P(x,y)\mathrm dx+Q(x,y)\mathrm dy=0,\,\frac{\partial Q}{\partial x}=\frac{\partial P}{\partial y}
$$
</div>

<div class="table-container">
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th style="text-align:center">常用公式总结</th>
<th style="text-align:center">常用公式总结</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:center">$y\mathrm dx+x\mathrm dy=\mathrm d(xy)$</td>
<td style="text-align:center">$\frac{y\mathrm dx-x\mathrm dy}{y^2}=\mathrm d\left(\frac{x}{y}\right)$</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:center">$\frac{y\mathrm dx-x\mathrm dy}{xy}=\mathrm d\left(\mathrm{ln}\left\vert\frac{x}{y}\right\vert\right)$</td>
<td style="text-align:center">$\frac{y\mathrm dx-x\mathrm dy}{x^2+y^2}=\mathrm d\left(\arctan\frac{x}{y}\right)$</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:center">$\frac{y\mathrm dx-x\mathrm dy}{x^2-y^2}=\frac{1}{2}\mathrm d\left(\ln\left\vert\frac{x-y}{x+y}\right\vert\right)$</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h3 id="7-4-积分因子"><a href="#7-4-积分因子" class="headerlink" title="7.4 积分因子"></a>7.4 积分因子</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\mu(x,y)P(x,y)\mathrm dx+\mu(x,y)Q(x,y)\mathrm dy=0,\,\frac{\partial(\mu Q)}{\partial x}=\frac{\partial(\mu P)}{\partial y}
$$
</div>

<ul>
<li><p>若$\frac{P’_y-Q’_x}{Q}=\varphi(x)$仅为$x$的函数，则$\mu(x)=\exp\left(\int\varphi(x)\mathrm dx\right)$</p>
</li>
<li><p>若$\frac{P’_y-Q’_x}{-P}=\psi(y)$仅为$y$的函数，则$\mu(y)=\exp\left(\int\psi(y)\mathrm dy\right)$</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="8-Gauss公式和Stokes公式"><a href="#8-Gauss公式和Stokes公式" class="headerlink" title="8. Gauss公式和Stokes公式"></a>8. Gauss公式和Stokes公式</h2><h3 id="8-1-Gauss公式"><a href="#8-1-Gauss公式" class="headerlink" title="8.1 Gauss公式"></a>8.1 Gauss公式</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\iint_{\partial\Omega}P\mathrm dy\land\mathrm dz+Q\mathrm dz\land\mathrm dx+R\mathrm dx\land\mathrm dy=\iiint_\Omega\left(\frac{\partial P}{\partial x}+\frac{\partial Q}{\partial y}+\frac{\partial R}{\partial z}\right)\mathrm dx\mathrm dy\mathrm dz
$$
</div>
<div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\iint_{\partial\Omega}\boldsymbol{v}\mathrm d\boldsymbol{S}=\iiint_\Omega\nabla\cdot\boldsymbol{v}\mathrm dx\mathrm dy\mathrm dz
$$
</div>


<h3 id="8-2-Stokes公式"><a href="#8-2-Stokes公式" class="headerlink" title="8.2 Stokes公式"></a>8.2 Stokes公式</h3><div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\oint_{\partial S}P\mathrm dx+Q\mathrm dy+R\mathrm dz=\iint_S(R'_y-Q'_z)\mathrm dy\land\mathrm dz+(P'_z-R'_x)\mathrm dz\land\mathrm dx+(Q'_y-P'_x)\mathrm dx\land\mathrm dy
$$
</div>
<div style="position:relative; height:100%; overflow-y:auto">
$$
\nabla\times\boldsymbol v=\mathrm{det}\begin{pmatrix}\boldsymbol{i} & \boldsymbol{j} & \boldsymbol{k} \\ \frac{\partial}{\partial x}&\frac{\partial}{\partial y}&\frac{\partial}{\partial z}\\P&Q&R\end{pmatrix},\\
\oint_{\partial S}\boldsymbol v\cdot\boldsymbol\tau\mathrm dl=\iint_S(\nabla\times\boldsymbol v)\cdot\boldsymbol n\mathrm dS
$$
</div>


<h3 id="8-3-空间向量场"><a href="#8-3-空间向量场" class="headerlink" title="8.3 空间向量场"></a>8.3 空间向量场</h3><ul>
<li><strong>面连通</strong>：$\Omega\subset\mathbb{R}^3$中任一封闭曲面$S$的内部都包含在$\Omega$中，则称$\Omega$是面（二维）连通区域</li>
<li><strong>线连通</strong>：$\Omega\subset\mathbb{R}^3$中任一简单闭曲线$L$，均有$\Omega$中曲面以$L$为边界，则称$\Omega$是线（一维）连通区域</li>
</ul>
<ol>
<li>连续保守场等价于有势场</li>
<li>线连通区域上的保守场等价于无旋场</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="9-非负项级数"><a href="#9-非负项级数" class="headerlink" title="9. 非负项级数"></a>9. 非负项级数</h2><h3 id="9-1-比较判别法"><a href="#9-1-比较判别法" class="headerlink" title="9.1 比较判别法"></a>9.1 比较判别法</h3><ul>
<li><p>普通形式</p>
<ul>
<li>$\forall n\in\mathbb{N},0\leq a_n\leq b_n,\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}b_n收敛\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n收敛$</li>
<li>$\forall n\in\mathbb{N},a_n\geq b_n\geq 0,\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}b_n发散\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n发散$</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>极限形式</p>
<p>$a_n&gt;0,b_n&gt;0,\lim\limits_{n\to\infty}\frac{a_n}{b_n}=\lambda,0\leq\lambda\leq+\infty$</p>
<ul>
<li>$\lambda&lt;\infty,\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}b_n收敛\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n收敛$</li>
<li>$\lambda&gt;0,\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}b_n发散\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n发散$</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="9-2-Cauchy根式判别法"><a href="#9-2-Cauchy根式判别法" class="headerlink" title="9.2 Cauchy根式判别法"></a>9.2 Cauchy根式判别法</h3><blockquote>
<p>$\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n$为非负项级数</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><p>普通形式</p>
<ul>
<li>$\forall n\in\mathbb{N},\sqrt[n]{a_n}&lt; r\leq1\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n收敛$</li>
<li>$\exists无穷多个n\in\mathbb{N},\sqrt[n]{a_n}\geq1\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n发散$</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>极限形式</p>
<p>$\lim\limits_{n\to\infty}\sqrt[n]{a_n}=q$</p>
<ul>
<li>$q&lt;1\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n收敛$</li>
<li>$q&gt;1\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n发散$</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="9-3-积分判别法"><a href="#9-3-积分判别法" class="headerlink" title="9.3 积分判别法"></a>9.3 积分判别法</h3><p>设$f(x)$在$[1,+\infty)$上单调下降且非负，则$\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}f(n)$与$\int_1^{+\infty}f(x)\mathrm dx$敛散性相同</p>
<blockquote>
<p>常用标尺：$\frac{1}{n^p},\frac{1}{n(\ln n)^p},\frac{1}{n\ln n(\ln\ln n)^p}$</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="9-4-比值判别法"><a href="#9-4-比值判别法" class="headerlink" title="9.4 比值判别法"></a>9.4 比值判别法</h3><blockquote>
<p> $\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n$与$\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}b_n$都是严格的正项级数</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li>$\forall n\in\mathbb{N},\frac{a_{n+1}}{a_n}\leq\frac{b_{n+1}}{b_n},且\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}b_n收敛\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n收敛$</li>
<li>$\forall n\in\mathbb{N},\frac{a_{n+1}}{a_n}\geq\frac{b_{n+1}}{b_n},且\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}b_n发散\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n发散$</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="9-5-D‘Alembert判别法"><a href="#9-5-D‘Alembert判别法" class="headerlink" title="9.5 D‘Alembert判别法"></a>9.5 D‘Alembert判别法</h3><blockquote>
<p>$\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n$为严格正项级数</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><p>普通形式</p>
<ul>
<li>$\forall n\geq n_0,\frac{a_{n+1}}{a_n}\leq r&lt;1\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n收敛$</li>
<li>$\forall n\geq n_0,\frac{a_{n+1}}{a_n}&gt;1\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n发散$</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>极限形式</p>
<p>$\lim\limits_{n\to\infty}\frac{a_{n+1}}{a_n}=q$</p>
<ul>
<li>$q&lt;1\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n收敛$</li>
<li>$q&gt;1\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n发散$</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="9-6-Raabe判别法"><a href="#9-6-Raabe判别法" class="headerlink" title="9.6 Raabe判别法"></a>9.6 Raabe判别法</h3><blockquote>
<p>$\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n$为严格正项级数</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><p>普通形式</p>
<ul>
<li>$\forall n\geq n_0,n\left(\frac{a_{n+1}}{a_n}-1\right)\geq q&gt;1\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n收敛$</li>
<li>$\forall n\geq n_0,n\left(\frac{a_{n+1}}{a_n}-1\right)\leq1\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n发散$</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p>极限形式</p>
<p>$\lim\limits_{n\to\infty}n\left(\frac{a_{n+1}}{a_n}-1\right)=q$</p>
<ul>
<li>$q&gt;1\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n收敛$</li>
<li>$q&lt;1\Rightarrow\sum\limits_{n=1}^{+\infty}a_n发散$</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
